We are creating this network to share the best of Black experiences with the diaspora. ALL content is created by Black Content Creators (filmakers, documentarians, Real Estate, Biblical and Black Diasporic Historians, Finance, Health/Wellness, Lifestyle, Music, Poetic Arts, Family, Clean Eating, etc.) sharing their best with us all.

We are asking that you support this independent Blac media outlet by purchasing a subscription, liking/sharing our IG page, help us get to 500 subscribers within our firts quarter, RECOMMEND Content Creators and suggestions for future programming.

Join us for our Virtual Pre-Launch event, July 28th at 7PM for more information DM or email us at support@sablenetwork.tv

IG: @sablenetworktv

@famjenks @tscllc  @sablenetworktv

node.text:
@wealth__forever - The only thing holding you back is your mindset and your ability to shift your thinking and your actions. I shifted from listening to the radio to listening to podcasts, I shifted from associating with fake & broke individuals to associating with business owners and solution oriented individuals. I shifted from playing video games, to reading books on real estate investing and financial literacy.

I shifted from brunch every weekend to weekend seminars on investing & personal development. Most importantly, I shifted from blaming my environment to taking full accountability for my actions and investing in becoming the best version of me for my family and community. You can make that shift too if you want it bad enough, I won’t say it was easy, but it was worth it. :  WEALTH FOREVER 🏚💰❗️. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ . . . .  #realestate #financialfreedom #financialliteracy #wealth #betonyourself #youngceo #htx #duval #atl #webuyhouses #househunter #businessquotes #businessowners #atlanta #wealthforever
